51:45.861 --> 51:49.427
And that's why they call it
the glove compartment.

51:53.351 --> 51:55.457
Trust you know
how to put those on?

52:03.120 --> 52:04.683
Herb, what are we doing?

52:04.707 --> 52:06.675
Shh, justice, come on.

52:10.748 --> 52:11.852
Come on.

52:13.958 --> 52:15.339
Shh.

52:28.904 --> 52:30.319
Herb...

52:54.792 --> 52:56.804
Look.

52:56.828 --> 52:58.209
Look.

53:03.490 --> 53:04.698
Oh, God.

53:15.433 --> 53:17.377
Well, I guess you're less
imposing to grown-ups.

53:17.401 --> 53:18.861
Who are you?
What do you want?

53:18.885 --> 53:20.621
Who are we?
What do we want?

53:20.645 --> 53:22.623
We want you.

53:22.647 --> 53:25.143
With a fucking gun?
Shut the fuck up

53:25.167 --> 53:26.386
and open your eyes.

53:26.410 --> 53:29.078
What?

53:29.102 --> 53:31.287
