53:33.865 --> 53:36.189
You disgusting monster!

53:37.490 --> 53:38.491
John?

53:39.906 --> 53:41.332
You dirty fuck!

53:41.356 --> 53:43.196
You piece of shit!

53:43.220 --> 53:45.094
Get the fuck up,
you dirty motherfucker.

53:45.118 --> 53:47.890
No! No! No!
You piece of... shit!

53:47.914 --> 53:49.236
I'll kill you!

53:49.260 --> 53:50.893
I'll kill you, you fucker.

53:50.917 --> 53:52.274
I'll fucking kill you!

53:52.298 --> 53:55.069
You dirty motherfucker!

53:55.093 --> 53:57.865
You fucking dirty
motherfucking...

53:57.889 --> 53:59.281
John. John!

53:59.305 --> 54:02.215
Fuck!
John, stop! Hey! Hey!

54:02.239 --> 54:04.078
That's enough!
That's enough!

54:04.102 --> 54:05.079
Stop.

54:06.829 --> 54:09.222
Shit, man, I thought you
were gonna kill him.

54:09.246 --> 54:11.948
Okay, I wasn't expecting that.

54:11.972 --> 54:13.433
Pretty impressive.

54:13.457 --> 54:15.297
Shit.

54:15.321 --> 54:17.230
What have I done?

54:17.254 --> 54:18.921
Is that why you brought me here?

54:18.945 --> 54:21.268
To beat the shit out of him,
is what you wanted me to do?

54:21.292 --> 54:24.340
Holy shit, what have I done?

54:24.364 --> 54:26.860
Nothing's gonna happen to you.

54:26.884 --> 54:29.345
What about him?

54:29.369 --> 54:32.521
We're not done with him yet.

54:32.545 --> 54:34.581
He's gonna get what he deserves.

54:50.217 --> 54:52.634
Let me take those for you.

55:10.962 --> 55:13.240
That's it.
Okay, just here.

55:16.589 --> 55:18.118
Now what?

55:18.142 --> 55:20.534
I got it from here,
you take a load off, champ.

55:20.558 --> 55:24.020
I'll be right back
with refreshments.

55:59.459 --> 56:01.195
Right on time.
No.

56:01.219 --> 56:02.265
What's wrong?

56:02.289 --> 56:03.957
What did you do to him?

56:03.981 --> 56:05.959
Oh, come on, you're smart enough

56:05.983 --> 56:08.271
for me not to have to explain.

56:08.295 --> 56:10.619
Here.
No, I can't.

56:10.643 --> 56:12.414
I won't.

56:12.438 --> 56:14.243
Don't go down this road, John,

56:14.267 --> 56:16.245
do not make this choice.

56:16.269 --> 56:18.972
I don't to do with whatever
you got going on down there.

56:18.996 --> 56:21.871
Jack Crane is a pedophile!

56:21.895 --> 56:24.391
We did society a favor!

56:24.415 --> 56:27.152
Yeah, how
do you feel, John, huh?

56:27.176 --> 56:28.637
How does that feel?

56:28.661 --> 56:31.122
'Cause that does not
get any better, trust me.

56:31.146 --> 56:35.644
John, do the right
thing, take control and drink.

56:35.668 --> 56:38.060
No.

56:38.084 --> 56:40.234
You need to understand
something, John,

56:40.258 --> 56:42.616
you are either with me
or you're against me.

56:42.640 --> 56:46.482
And, believe me, you do not
want to be against me.

56:47.852 --> 56:49.347
You leave me out of this.

56:49.371 --> 56:51.901
Don't you ever come near me
again, do you hear me?

56:51.925 --> 56:53.410
Do you hear me?

56:57.241 --> 56:58.587
What a waste.

